text: "XXX" is a 2017 song by Kendrick Lamar featuring U2. It is the eleventh track from his fourth studio album Damn and went to number 50 in the United Kingdom, number 33 in the United States, number 22 in Ireland, number 36 in Canada, number 82 in Sweden, number 30 in Portugal and number 31 in New Zealand. == References == Category:2017 songs Category:Kendrick Lamar songs Category:U2 songs Category:Rap songs
title: XXX (Kendrick Lamar song)
